The '''Ammuud clans''' were feudal families that governed the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ammuud/Legends|Ammuud]]. The [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] demanded that each clan provide forces for [[Spaceport/Legends|port]] security. Two of the most prominent clans were [[Reesbon clan|House Reesbon]] and [[House Glayyd]].

